OL,3,CNurses face 'abhorrent' levels of
OL,4,Cviolence as A&E attacks double in five
OL,5,Cyears
OL,7,FThe nursing union submitted Freedom of
OL,8,Finformation (FOI) requests to NHS
OL,9,Fhospitals with accident and emergency
OL,10,Fdepartments and found rates of
OL,11,Fviolence towards staff had almost
OL,12,Fdoubled in the last five years.
OL,14,FFigures from 89 hospital trusts, out
OL,15,Fof a possible 129, revealed there were
OL,16,F4,054 cases of physical violence
OL,17,Fagainst A&E staff recorded in 2024, up
OL,18,Ffrom 2,093 in 2019.
