OL,5,Cyears
OL,7,FWithout action to tackle long waits,
OL,8,Fcorridor care and "chronic" staffing
OL,9,Fproblems, the rates of violence will
OL,10,Fcontinue to rise, the RCN warned.
OL,12,FOne senior A&E nurse based in east
OL,13,FLondon told the RCN she has seen
OL,14,Fcolleagues punched and kicked and
OL,15,Fdescribed how a colleague had a gun
OL,16,Fpointed at them.
OL,18,FShe herself had been spat at by a
OL,19,Fpatient and threatened with an acid
OL,20,Fattack.
