OL,7,FA senior charge nurse from the East
OL,8,FMidlands, Rachelle McCarthy, told the
OL,9,FRCN that "even patients you would
OL,10,Fexpect to be placid are becoming irate
OL,11,Fbecause of just how long they have to
OL,12,Fwait".
OL,14,F"You can only imagine the behaviour of
OL,15,Fthose who are already prone to
OL,16,Fviolence," she added.
OL,18,FMs McCarthy also told the union she
OL,19,Fwas punched "square in the face" by a
OL,20,F"drunk, six foot two bloke".
