OL,7,FAnother nurse said: "It's not going to
OL,8,Fhelp with our retention and
OL,9,Frecruitment if you think you're going
OL,10,Fto be clobbered every shift."
OL,12,FSarah Tappy, a senior sister in an A&E
OL,13,Fin east London, was knocked
OL,14,Funconscious after being punched in the
OL,15,Fhead by a patient.
OL,17,F"The violence is awful," she said.
OL,18,F"And it's just constant. Nurses,
OL,19,Fdoctors, receptionists, none of us
OL,20,Ffeels safe."
