OL,7,FRCN general secretary and chief
OL,8,Fexecutive Professor Nicola Ranger
OL,9,Fsaid: "Nursing staff not only go to
OL,10,Fwork underpaid and undervalued but now
OL,11,Fface a rising tide of violence."
OL,13,F"It leads to both physical and mental
OL,14,Fscarring, lengthy time off and
OL,15,Fsometimes staff never returning."
