OL,5,Cyears
OL,7,F"Measures to keep staff safe day-to-
OL,8,Fday are crucial, but the stark reality
OL,9,Fis that unless the Government does
OL,10,Fsomething about lengthy waits,
OL,11,Fcorridor care and understaffed nursing
OL,12,Fteams, more nursing staff will become
OL,13,Fvictims of this utterly abhorrent
OL,14,Fbehaviour."
OL,16,F"Left unaddressed, this could see
OL,17,Fplans to reform the NHS fail
OL,18,Fcompletely."
