OL,7,FThe Liberal Democrats have called for
OL,8,FA&E staff to be given access to a
OL,9,Fpanic button which would give them a
OL,10,F"direct line" to the police.
OL,12,FThe party's health spokesperson Helen
OL,13,FMorgan said: "The Government must
OL,14,Furgently ensure all A&E units have a
OL,15,Fdirect line to their nearest police
OL,16,Fstation through a panic button ... to
OL,17,Fprotect patients and staff and ensure
OL,18,Fthese violent criminals are swiftly
OL,19,Farrested."
