OL,7,FHealth Secretary Wes Streeting said:
OL,8,F"I am appalled by these findings.
OL,9,FNurses dedicate their lives to helping
OL,10,Fothers and deserve to go about their
OL,11,Fjobs free from violence or
OL,12,Fintimidation.
OL,14,F"Anyone who violates this core
OL,15,Fprinciple will feel the full force of
OL,16,Fthe law."
