OL,7,F"I met with the Royal College of
OL,8,FNursing recently to reaffirm our
OL,9,Fcommitment to standing with frontline
OL,10,Fworkers, working together to stop
OL,11,Fviolence against NHS staff and
OL,12,Fimproving their working conditions."
OL,14,F"Just yesterday I announced a new
OL,15,Fgraduate guarantee to get more nurses
OL,16,Finto our NHS, and I have also
OL,17,Fcommitted to shining a light on the
OL,18,Fextent to which corridor care plagues
OL,19,Four NHS, as the first step to
OL,20,Feradicating it."
